In order to gain her attention=2C the little boy decides to construct a co=
stume=2C a sort of enormous mask that would transform him into a bird =E2=
=80=94 a giant=2C trembling=2C clumsy bird incapable of flight=2C which is=
 surely how one feels when faced with unrequited love. Still=2C enveloped=
 by the shiny feathers=2C he feels handsome =E2=80=94 he feels worthier of=
 Sylvia=E2=80=99s attention and affection than in his own creaturely self.

