0%;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #C33737;text-decoration: underline;">=
<strong><em>Time Travel</em></strong></a> =E2=80=94 the kind of book that=
 lodges itself in the imagination=2C planting seeds of ideas=2C insights=
=2C and revelations bound to go on blossoming for the remainder of this li=
fetime =E2=80=94 with Bertrand Russell on <a href=3D"http://brainpickings.=
us2.list-manage.com/track/click?u=3D13eb080d8a315477042e0d5b1&id=3D4c1a2f7=
470&e=3Da5eb5cdf67" style=3D"-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;-ms-text-size=
-adjust: 100%;color: #C33737;text-decoration: underline;">the nature of ti=
me</a> and Virginia Woolf on <a href=3D"http://brainpickings.us2.list-mana=
ge1.com/track/click?u=3D13eb080d8a315477042e0d5b1&id=3D5fe97adfcb&e=3D=
